The match was part of the ICC Men's T20 World Cup 2022-23.
Netherlands have won back-to-back games against UAE and Namibia.
Netherlands chased down the target of 122 runs in 19.3 overs.
The win places Netherlands at the very top of their group.
Netherlands earned 2 points for the win, while Namibia earned 0 points.

Namibia won the toss and elected to bat first.
